_:N6203b2501a82469fb2ec87fbf0187288 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Sir Stephen Timms was appointed Minister of State in the Department for Work and Pensions, and the Department for Education, on 8 July 2024. He was elected as the MP for East Ham in July 2024.</p>\n" .
